<span class="name western">Muhammad Z Chauhan</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, MS</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Harvey and Bernice Jones Eye Institute, University of Arkansas for Medical Sciences, Little Rock, Arkansas</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Chauhan%20MZ"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Muhammad Z Chauhan</span></a>
