<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Elhusseiny%20AM"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Abdelrahman M Elhusseiny</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Abdelrahman M Elhusseiny</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, MSc</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Harvey and Bernice Jones Eye Institute, University of Arkansas for Medical Sciences, Little Rock, Arkansas</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Elhusseiny%20AM"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Abdelrahman M Elhusseiny</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Marwah%20S"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Shikha Marwah</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Shikha Marwah</span>, <span class="degrees">MS</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Ophthalmology and Visual Sciences, Kellogg Eye Center, University of Michigan, Ann Arbor, Michigan</div>
