<h3>
<span class="name western">Ahmed B Sallam</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, PhD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Harvey and Bernice Jones Eye Institute, University of Arkansas for Medical Sciences, Little Rock, Arkansas</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Sallam%20AB"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Ahmed B Sallam</span></a>
